{
  "stem": "8916.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a 19-year-old, strong young man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he-- you know, during a wartime, when invading armies are about to, you know, invade or about to enter, the people take to the road.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They try to outrun the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They try to find a safer place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hershel went east as fast as he could.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he did outrun the German army, up on the Soviet side, where his grandparents lived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Narewka.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So during that period of time, between 1939 and 1941, he was living in-- on the Soviet side.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he also spent some time in the Soviet Union, working.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then he became ill.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had an operation-- and this is what we've heard after the war-- and came back to Narewka in 1941, to his grandparents, to recuperate.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1941, he was 21.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he met the same fate as the rest of the population [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in 1941, when the Germans invaded and the special troops murdered everyone in town, including him.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he's in the common grave, in Narewka.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yep, that's right, and to everyone else that I remember in my mind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so we were the four of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my sister, my older sister, got-- also got a job that was outside of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She worked in a company called Kabelwerk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's a-- a company that did electrical-- made electrical parts, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] various kinds of cables and connections and things like that, and plugs.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a war-related factory, so she got a job and she was able to also get out of the ghetto and come back.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But soon they created a camp around or near the company.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
